data.meta_description:
1,462 likes, 9 comments - hollywoodreporter on July 15, 2024: "Optimism in the face of uncertainty was the tune of the day last week at the #SocialImpactSummit.⁠
⁠
The summit focused on “The Future of Hollywood Philanthropy,” and buzzed with hope and urgency. #SharonStone, #CharlizeTheron, #UzoAduba, #WilsonCruz, #ThomasSadoski and #JulieBowen were among the stars who took part in the summit, where #FeedingAmerica was honored as THR’s Philanthropic Organization of the Year.⁠
⁠
Read more about the inaugural summit, and what the stars had to say at the link in bio. #SIFTHR_Impact".
